/n68co2/hitran2016

This folder contains correlated-k distributions for CO2.
Not all can or should be used for proper radiative transfer calculations.
Some very much shouldn't be used!  But for now, I keep the collection of files
to be used for comparisons, validation and the like.

Unless noted, all files contain 61 pressures, 17 temperatures.  
Further descriptions are listed below.


!! Version for use with src.n68equiv radiation package
Nnu1e4_c500_subL_q1_grrtm - - 1e4 sampling points per spectral interval,
                    500 cm-1 cutoff, chiPH89__CO2-CO2 subLorentzian
                    lineshape, qalpha = 1, rrtm gauss pt grid

!! Others
Nnu1e4_c500_subL_q0_phCO2-N2_grrtm - 1e4 sampling points per spectral interval,
                    500 cm-1 cutoff, chiPH89__CO2-N2 subLorentzian
                    lineshape, qalpha = 0, rrtm gauss pt grid

Nnu1e4_c500_subL_q0_grrtm - 1e4 sampling points per spectral interval,
                    500 cm-1 cutoff, chiPH89__CO2-CO2 subLorentzian
                    lineshape, qalpha = 0, rrtm gauss pt grid


Nnu1e4_c500_subL_q0_gclima - 1e4 sampling points per spectral interval,
                    500 cm-1 cutoff, chiPH89__CO2-CO2 subLorentzian
                    lineshape, qalpha = 0, rrtm gauss pt grid

Nnu1e4_c500_subL_q1_gclima - 1e4 sampling points per spectral interval,
                    500 cm-1 cutoff, chiPH89__CO2-CO2 subLorentzian
                    lineshape, qalpha = 1, clima gauss pt grid

Nnu1e4_c1000_subL_q1_gclima - 1e4 sampling points per spectral interval,
                    1000 cm-1 cutoff, chiPH89__CO2-CO2 subLorentzian
                    lineshape, qalpha = 1, clima gauss pt grid

Nnu1e5_c500_subL_q1_gclima - 1e5 sampling points per spectral interval,
                    500 cm-1 cutoff, chiPH89__CO2-CO2 subLorentzian
                    lineshape, qalpha = 1, clima gauss pt grid

!! NOT Recommended. These use voigt lineshape k-distributions
Nnu1e4_c500_voigt_q0_grrtm - 1e4 sampling points per spectral interval, 
                    500 cm-1 cutoff, voigt lineshape, 
                    qalpha = 0, rrtm gauss pt grid

Nnu1e4_c50_voigt_q0_grrtm  - 1e4 sampling points per spectrla interval, 
                    50 cm-1 wing cutoff, voigt lineshape
                    qalpha = 0, rrtm_gauss pt grid

Nnu1e4_c25_voigt_q0_grrtm  - 1e4 sampling points per spectrla interval,
                    25 cm-1 wing cutoff, voigt lineshape
                    qalpha = 0, rrtm_gauss pt grid
